query:
INSERT INTO hotels (tripId, name, address, checkInDate, checkInTime, checkOutDate, checkOutTime, confirmationNumber, phone, website, price, currency, category, paymentStatus, coverImage, parkingImage, gallery, notes, linkedDocumentId, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT 2 as tripId, name, address, checkInDate, checkInTime, checkOutDate, checkOutTime, confirmationNumber, phone, website, price, currency, category, paymentStatus, coverImage, parkingImage, gallery, notes, linkedDocumentId, NOW() as createdAt, NOW() as updatedAt
FROM hotels
WHERE tripId = 1;
